# Dude environment configuration
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in values as needed.

# VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY (optional): enables the smart assist features
# (proposal summaries and client-email drafting).
# Leave unset to run Dude fully offline — the assist actions simply hide.
# A Gemini API key can be generated from Google AI for Developers (ai.google.dev).
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=""
